- **Deliverables:** Integration architecture, predictive models, security compliance reports
- **Dependencies:** Data integration completion, model training data, security framework validation

**Month 11-12: Enterprise-Wide Deployment**
- **Objective:** Achieve enterprise-wide deployment and measure comprehensive impact
- **Key Activities:**
  - [ ] Complete enterprise-wide tool deployment
  - [ ] Implement advanced AI governance controls
  - [ ] Establish continuous improvement processes
  - [ ] Conduct comprehensive ROI assessment
  - [ ] Plan Phase 3 innovation initiatives

**Milestone 2B-2:** Enterprise Deployment Complete
- **Success Criteria:** 85% enterprise adoption, ROI targets achieved, governance operational
- **Deliverables:** Enterprise deployment report, ROI analysis, Phase 3 strategic plan
- **Dependencies:** Organizational readiness, resource availability, strategic alignment

