## 3. Resource Requirements and Dependencies

### 3.1 Human Resources

**Core Implementation Team (Phase 1)**
- **AI Program Director** (1 FTE) - Strategic oversight and stakeholder management
- **Technical Lead** (1 FTE) - Architecture and integration leadership
- **Security Lead** (1 FTE) - Security and compliance oversight
- **Change Management Lead** (1 FTE) - Organizational change and adoption
- **Training Lead** (1 FTE) - Capability development and user enablement
- **Project Manager** (1 FTE) - Program coordination and delivery management

**Expanded Team (Phase 2-3)**
- **AI Engineers** (3-5 FTE) - Tool integration and development
- **Data Scientists** (2-3 FTE) - Analytics and optimization
- **DevOps Engineers** (2 FTE) - Infrastructure and deployment
- **User Experience Designers** (2 FTE) - Interface and workflow design
- **Business Analysts** (3-5 FTE) - Process analysis and optimization

**Total Resource Estimate:** 15-25 FTE across 24-month implementation

### 3.2 Financial Resources

**Implementation Costs (24 months)**
- **Personnel Costs:** $3.5M - $5.2M (fully loaded costs)
- **Infrastructure Costs:** $800K - $1.2M (cloud, security, monitoring)
- **Tool Licensing:** $400K - $600K (enterprise licenses and support)
- **Training and Development:** $300K - $500K (programs and materials)
- **Consulting and External Support:** $500K - $800K (specialized expertise)

**Total Investment:** $5.5M - $8.3M over 24 months
**Expected ROI:** 300-500% within 18-24 months
**Net Present Value:** $7.5M - $12.5M over 3 years

### 3.3 Technical Dependencies

**Infrastructure Requirements**
- **Cloud Platform:** GPU-accelerated instances (NVIDIA A100 or equivalent)
- **Storage:** High-performance object storage (10-50TB initial)
- **Network:** High-bandwidth connectivity (10Gbps minimum)
- **Security:** Zero-trust architecture with advanced threat protection
- **Monitoring:** Comprehensive observability and alerting platform

**Integration Dependencies**
- **API Management:** Enterprise API gateway and management platform
- **Identity Management:** Single sign-on and identity federation
- **Data Platform:** Modern data lake and analytics infrastructure
- **CI/CD Pipeline:** Automated deployment and testing infrastructure

### 3.4 Organizational Dependencies

**Executive Sponsorship**
- **C-Level Commitment:** CEO/CIO sponsorship and active involvement
- **Budget Approval:** Full program funding secured
- **Strategic Alignment:** AI strategy aligned with business objectives
- **Change Authorization:** Authority to implement organizational changes

**Stakeholder Engagement**
- **Department Leadership:** Active participation and support
- **End Users:** Willingness to adopt new tools and processes
- **IT Leadership:** Technical infrastructure and security support
- **Legal/Compliance:** Regulatory and risk management guidance

